ROLSCREEN COMPANY v. KIRSCH COMPANY. No. 7508. Circuit Court of Appeals, Sixth Circuit. Oct. 12, 1938. Bair, Freeman & Sinclair, of Des Moines, Iowa, and Frank E. Li veranee, Jr., of Grand Rapids, Mich., for appellant* Chappell & Earl, of Kalamazoo, Mich., for appellee.

Before PUCKS, SIMONS, and HAMILTON, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Upon motion of appellant it is ordered that this appeal be and the same is dismissed.
